Class ProxyManager<T extends SonarObject>

java.lang.Object
us.mn.state.dot.tms.client.proxy.ProxyManager<T>
Direct Known Subclasses:
AlertManager, ControllerManager, DeviceManager, IncidentManager, LCSIManager, ParkingAreaManager, PlanManager, R_NodeManager
public abstract class ProxyManager<T extends SonarObject> extends Object
A proxy manager is a container for SONAR proxy objects. It places each proxy into an appropriate style list model.
Author:
Douglas Lau
